root: ^You and Aether spent the rest of your days together. You taught them about your detective business, and they took you to all of their favorite concerts.

^You two hid up in the rafters, but Aether didn't mind having someone else up there with them. You offered them a job at your detective business, but they refused and continued to make music, but you were able to supply them with a brand new studio closer to home, with all the music equipment they could have ever wanted.
^You might not understand her music, but you're beginning to enjoy it, and you love every minute you spend jamming out with them.
